description: PM Modi's J&K Visit LIVE Updates: Security has been tightened across the Union Territory after a powerful explosion was heard early Sunday in a village in Jammu’s Bishnah, which is nearly 8-km away from Palli in the Samba district where Prime Minister Narendra Modi will visit.
